    progressionIntro: "Progress more conservatively during a deficit. Protect training quality before adding work.", progression: ["Try to match the prior session before demanding an increase.", "Add one repetition only when the set remains technically consistent.", "Increase load after all sets reach the top of the range, but use the smallest jump available.", "If strength falls across several lifts for two weeks, review sleep, deficit size, and training volume rather than adding conditioning."],
