    progressionIntro: "Use training performance as the main feedback signal. Recomposition rarely needs weekly program changes.",
    progression: ["Keep the same load until all working sets reach the top of the repetition range with stable technique.", "Increase by the smallest practical amount, then return to the lower end of the range.", "If strength is stable while measurements or photos improve, the plan is working even when scale weight is flat.", "If several lifts decline for two weeks, review recovery and nutrition before adding volume."],
